window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The complete series in a single offering!</p> <p>Blake never expected to meet beautiful women while studying archaeology â€” let alone a stunning Valkyrie.</p> <p>Dying was a bit of a bummer, but the chance to see Asgard with his own eyes was well worth it. Blake found himself one of the few, modern mortals found worthy of Valhalla, earning him the interest of the gorgeous battle maidens.</p> <p>But there's no time for feasting! Loki has broken free from his ancient prison, and Ragnarok is about to begin! Now, Blake will have to adapt to the brutal culture he studied and level up to survive the Twilight of the Gods.</p>"; 
